parameters.name: MASS
parameters.description:
Mass number of species                                
                              4  He+                                          
                             12  C+                                           
                             14  N+                                           
                             16  O+                                           
                             28  CO++N2+                                      
                             30  NO+                                          
                             32  O2+                                          
                             44  CO2+

parameters.name: BDATE
parameters.description: Beginning Date YYDDD - YY  = last two digits of year DDD = day of year .

parameters.name: BTIME
parameters.description:
Beginning Time - HH:MM:SS  - HH = hour                                 
                                    MM = minutes                              
                                    SS = seconds.

parameters.name: EDATE
parameters.description: Ending Date YYDDD - YY  = last two digits of year DDD = day of year.

parameters.name: ETIME
parameters.description:
Ending Time - HH:MM:SS - HH = hour         
                                                 MM = minutes      
                                                 SS = seconds.
